data.description:
Are you looking for Peace and Quiet? Look NO further as we are offering a true PONDEROSA FILLED
RETREAT for you to call home! Just 10 Min from Williams' Famous/Historic Route 66-Downtown!
This home sits on 1.04 Acres! Workshop, Storage Shed, New exterior Paint on Main House! New Light Fixtures both interior and exterior! New Switches & Outlets, Bluetooth Lights in Bathrooms, New Faucets & Drains, Re-Finished Bathtubs, New Thermostat and More! Come take a peek for yourself!
